import Control.Applicative
import Control.Monad
import System.IO


main :: IO ()
main = do
    n_temp <- getLine
    let n = read n_temp :: Int
    puzzle_temp <- getMultipleLines n
    let puzzle = map ( map ( read :: String -> Int ) . words ) puzzle_temp
    -- your code goes here

getMultipleLines :: Int -> IO [String]

getMultipleLines n
    | n <= 0 = return []
    | otherwise = do          
        x <- getLine         
        xs <- getMultipleLines (n-1)    
        let ret = (x:xs)    
        return ret

model.lua_template:
n = io.read("*number", "*l")
puzzle = {}
for puzzle_i = 1,n do
	puzzle_temp = io.read()
	puzzle_j = 1
	puzzle[puzzle_i] = {}
	for token in string.gmatch(puzzle_temp, "[^%s]+") do
		puzzle[puzzle_i][puzzle_j] = token
		puzzle_j = puzzle_j + 1
	end
end
